<subSubSection pageNumber="597" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="597">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Note:</emphasis>
The correct name in 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Belamcanda" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Belamcanda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.)" authorityName="" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Belamcanda" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">B. chinensis</emphasis>
(L.)
</taxonomicName>
A. DC. However, if 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Belamcanda" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Belamcanda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is subsumed within 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Iris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Iris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as favoured by Goldblatt &amp; Mabberley (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Novon</emphasis>
15: 128-132. 2005), the correct name for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Ixia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Ixia chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.) Goldblatt &amp; Mabb." authorityName="Goldblatt &amp; Mabb." baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Iris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="domestica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="597">Iris domestica</emphasis>
(L.) Goldblatt &amp; Mabb.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
